subject: Tennis
Sony Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Serena Williams capitalized on a critical double fault by Yaroslava Shvedova to survive a 69-minute first set and win, 7-6 (7), 6-2, at the Sony Open in Key Biscayne, Fla.
